<plot>High Falls explores the relationship between a married couple and their best friend as they navigate the problem of communication in a world without a moral center. The husband and wife each separately divulge secrets to the friend, and for the next 24 hours he holds these two secrets as he watches the couple's inability to honestly connect.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?238781</url></doc>
